    • Constructor Detail

      • PacketsTeam

        public PacketsTeam(java.lang.String name,
                   org.bukkit.entity.Player player)
        Create a team with packets. Call create() to send the to viewers players
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the team (can't be changed after)
        suffix - The suffix of the team (after the player's name)
        displayName - The display name of the team (on the right scoreboard for example)
        prefix - The prefix of the team (before the player's name)
        players - The players into the team
        viewers - The players who can see the team . Set to null for all connected players
